{"type":"message","id":"d9d7bfb2","parentId":"3e29e861","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:29:39.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to search for information about our job positions using \"multi-search-engine-simple\" and then learn, understand, and memorize the results. Let me first check if there's a skill or tool available for this, and also search memory for context about what these positions are.\n\nLet me look at what tools I have and search for relevant information. The \"multi-search-engine-simple\" sounds like it could be a web search capability. Let me check if there's a skill for this - the agent-reach skill covers web search functionality.\n\nActually, let me first search my memory for context about these positions, and also try to use web_fetch to search for information about qualification agency (资质代办) job positions.\n\n\nI'll start by searching for information about 资质代办 companies and their role structures to understand what each position does.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"先搜索一下资质代办行业的职位信息，然后整理学习。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_42867d4aa09345a38f7bb2ce","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E8%B5%84%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A3%E5%8A%9E%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A+%E5%B2%97%E4%BD%8D%E8%81%8C%E8%B4%A3+%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84","maxChars":5000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_219e5ed99173417593a10d4f","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.zhipin.com/web/geek/job?query=%E8%B5%84%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A3%E5%8A%9E&scene=0","maxChars":5000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_71336d61279a4b1bb06f1f61","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"团队岗位 职位职责 资质代办 SOP"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":22187,"output":629,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22816,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timest